      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "691917",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "GXG",
        "uid": "97770"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t体制内不会反抗，只会非暴力不合作。有钱花的坐在办公室里等下班，没钱花的用手里的权力寻租赚钱，反正不会听一个发不出工资的包子的命令\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-09-25",
      "agree_count": 4,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "691921",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "sougoushurufa",
        "uid": "114980"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t不会的，还有罚款权呢。只是合法的手段不能用了而已，等着罚款吧。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-09-25",
